WEBVTT

00:02.980 --> 00:04.694
<i>Previously on</i> Camelot...

00:04.866 --> 00:06.433
My father, he sent me

00:06.501 --> 00:08.735
to tell you that men are
attacking Bardon Pass.

00:08.803 --> 00:10.921
We lose that, word will spread
of our weakness,

00:10.946 --> 00:12.382
and all our land could
come under threat.

00:12.674 --> 00:15.075
If this is done well,
the only safe place

00:15.143 --> 00:16.807
in the kingdom will
be under my protection.

00:16.832 --> 00:18.635
The crown will fall to me.

00:19.147 --> 00:20.811
Did something happen
between you and the king?

00:20.836 --> 00:22.536
I did a terrible thing,

00:22.550 --> 00:25.419
but I'm still your wife!
You're not my wife;

00:25.486 --> 00:27.688
you're the king's whore.
Cover this up,

00:27.755 --> 00:30.624
or risk losing everything.
What did you do?!

00:30.692 --> 00:32.692
It was the morning
of my wedding.

00:32.759 --> 00:35.762
He had her first.
And then he married us.

00:35.830 --> 00:38.331
- What about Morgan?
- We go to Castle Pendragon--

00:38.399 --> 00:41.401
bring her back before the king
to answer for her treason.

00:41.469 --> 00:44.070
While the entire country
bleeds, you storm in here

00:44.095 --> 00:45.500
with your insane charges.

00:45.907 --> 00:48.275
I will expose the corruption
of this sorcerer.

00:48.342 --> 00:52.412
Let all who seek a safe harbour
find one with me.

00:56.617 --> 00:58.452
Take Kay; take the family.

00:58.519 --> 01:00.454
I'll create a diversion
from the front. Go.

01:00.521 --> 01:03.423
I'll be right behind you.
King Arthur dies at our hands.

01:03.491 --> 01:06.259
Here. Tonight.

01:08.896 --> 01:12.899
♪

